The Castelblanco Law Group is a California-based law office concentrating on renter rights and personal injury cases. They focus on representing customers taking care of substandard living problems, such as parasite infestations and lead poisoning, along with those harmed in no-fault car accidents. The firm is multilingual, offering services in both English and Spanish, and has obtained over $200 million in settlements for their customers. They are dedicated to boosting the lifestyle for occupants and making certain justice for personal injury victims.
